description: Baker and decorator of some of THE BEST sweet treats you will ever eat! And we're taking them to the streets! Look for LizzieCakes on the streets near you! From our award winning "Banana Pudding Cheesecake" to our delicious S'mores Cookies that are sure to spark memories but with a twist, you're gonna love it all.  Catch us at a rally near you, or even better yet, ask us about catering your next event!
name: LizzieCakes, LLC
